{"tid":1321333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重溫]當年台灣貼滿成架TVB採訪車都係memo紙","createTime":"2019-07-15T15:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T21:11:31.000Z","uid":55650,"like":61,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b1aab8c035ac6014f9e73eaa8c147d3ea0ff6c0b","tid":1321333,"uid":55650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:41:04.000Z","msg":"重溫下當年台灣太陽花新聞先<br />\n學運己進入第八日，早上參與人數明顯減少，記者途經立法院門前發現台灣TVBS電視台採訪車被貼上MEMO紙，據了解，事因該電視台報道學運站場過份偏頗，有做假新聞之嫌，群眾貼上MEMO紙以示不滿。<br />\n<br />\nTVBS的SNG車也同樣被貼滿大小不一的「貼紙」，寫著「謝謝TVBS記者辛苦做假新聞給我爸媽看」、「說好的真相呢？」、「你們赤化了嗎？」、「別把自己搞的這麼丟臉」、「我ㄉ太陽餅呢？」等反諷字句，以示對T台的抗議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fvs3RWe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffvs3RWe.jpg&h=ea357912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VLJbgnY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVLJbgnY.jpg&h=925fc119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KdYyuHZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKdYyuHZ.jpg&h=0004c42a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新聞重溫網址︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/765153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpaper%2F765153&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=c8e71ef7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpaper%2F765153&h=0111474d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/765153</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://mcnews.cc/p/5465\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmcnews.cc%2Fp%2F5465&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=0f6eed49\" target=\"_blank\">https://mcnews.cc/p/5465</a><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好咁做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db02be4e625f97b514184